sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant A as Caller Service
  participant BH as Bulkhead (permits)
  participant D as Downstream

  C->>A: GET /call/slow
  A->>BH: try_acquire(slow permits)
  alt permits available
    BH-->>A: acquired
    A->>D: request (timeout)
    alt success
      D-->>A: 200 OK
      A-->>C: 200 OK
    else failure/timeout
      D-->>A: 5xx/timeout
      A-->>C: fallback or 503
    end
    A->>BH: release permit
  else saturated
    BH-->>A: rejected
    A-->>C: 429/503 fail-fast (capacity preserved)
  end
